[
  {
    "startTime": 13.568,
    "endTime": 16.601,
    "text": "(Cello music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.12,
    "endTime": 67.892,
    "text": "(Music ends)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.373,
    "endTime": 71.751,
    "text": "On the flight here,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.71,
    "endTime": 74.79199999999999,
    "text": "I was reminded about my mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.437,
    "endTime": 78.69,
    "text": "I'm a self-taught cellist, I've never had a lesson."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.93,
    "endTime": 81.66900000000001,
    "text": "I studied double bass, but I just picked up the cello and started playing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.693,
    "endTime": 82.883,
    "text": "because I love doing it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.907,
    "endTime": 84.693,
    "text": "But my mom was an inspiration to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.717,
    "endTime": 86.781,
    "text": "I did not realize she was an inspiration,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.805,
    "endTime": 90.93400000000001,
    "text": "because she got her music degree through a mail-order course,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.958,
    "endTime": 92.426,
    "text": "the US School of Music."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.45,
    "endTime": 94.21000000000001,
    "text": "While raising two kids,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.863,
    "endTime": 97.966,
    "text": "she received a lesson a week in the mail,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.99,
    "endTime": 99.14,
    "text": "and practiced."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.165,
    "endTime": 102.727,
    "text": "And at the end of a couple of years, she put on a recital."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.751,
    "endTime": 106.774,
    "text": "And I'll be 50 this month, and it took me that long to realize"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.799,
    "endTime": 108.71900000000001,
    "text": "that she was that big of an inspiration."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.357,
    "endTime": 111.687,
    "text": "I'm just going to keep -- yeah, thanks, mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.6,
    "endTime": 118.24799999999999,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.532,
    "endTime": 121.192,
    "text": "She's also one of the most extraordinary people I know,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.217,
    "endTime": 123.485,
    "text": "beyond being a wonderful musician."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.913,
    "endTime": 127.222,
    "text": "I want to play a little bit for mom and your moms as well, actually."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.968,
    "endTime": 130.72,
    "text": "(Cello music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.66,
    "endTime": 144.142,
    "text": "(Music ends)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.307,
    "endTime": 147.196,
    "text": "You know, when you normally hear a cello, you think of this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.221,
    "endTime": 149.745,
    "text": "(Plays Bach Cello Suite No.1)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.77,
    "endTime": 151.971,
    "text": "We're not going to do that today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.996,
    "endTime": 155.79000000000002,
    "text": "(Laughter and applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.328,
    "endTime": 158.304,
    "text": "(Drums)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.684,
    "endTime": 163.684,
    "text": "(Cello)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.489,
    "endTime": 167.639,
    "text": "Hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.76,
    "endTime": 170.476,
    "text": "(Looped samples of onstage sounds)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.282,
    "endTime": 187.257,
    "text": "(Cello music and looped samples)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.911,
    "endTime": 236.911,
    "text": "(Music ends)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.805,
    "endTime": 244.76600000000002,
    "text": "(Applause and cheers)"
  }
]